Sentencas: Hierarchically-ordered NiO-Ce0.8Gd0.2O1.9 (GDC) composite anode powders were synthesized using eggshell membranes as biotemplates.
Titulo: Eggshell-membrane-templated synthesis of hierarchically-ordered NiO-Ce0.8Gd0.2O1.9 composite powders and their electrochemical performances as SOFC anodes

Sentencas: The morphology of the as-synthesized powders depended on the kind of Ni precursor and the use of EDTA as a chelating agent.
Titulo: Eggshell-membrane-templated synthesis of hierarchically-ordered NiO-Ce0.8Gd0.2O1.9 composite powders and their electrochemical performances as SOFC anodes

Sentencas: Hierarchically-ordered anode powders were obtained from Ni chloride and Ni acetate precursors with EDTA.
Titulo: Eggshell-membrane-templated synthesis of hierarchically-ordered NiO-Ce0.8Gd0.2O1.9 composite powders and their electrochemical performances as SOFC anodes

Sentencas: The Ni GDC anode synthesized from Ni chloride precursor with EDTA exhibited the lowest polarization resistance at 800 degrees C and an activation energy of 0.01 Omega cm(2) and 0.74 eV, respectively, in humidified H-2.
Titulo: Eggshell-membrane-templated synthesis of hierarchically-ordered NiO-Ce0.8Gd0.2O1.9 composite powders and their electrochemical performances as SOFC anodes

Sentencas: In accordance with the polarization resistance results, the 0.5-mm thick GDC electrolyte-supported single cell with the Ni-GDC anode synthesized from Ni chloride precursor with EDTA showed a maximum power density of 0.34 W cm(-2) at 800 degrees C with humidified H-2 fuel.
Titulo: Eggshell-membrane-templated synthesis of hierarchically-ordered NiO-Ce0.8Gd0.2O1.9 composite powders and their electrochemical performances as SOFC anodes
